T02TD1756E:234b-1: ma h'a k'a la aa bhi sa ma ya /
T02TD1756E:234b-3: nag po chen po'i mngon par rtogs pa /
T02TD1756E:234b-4: dpal nag po chen po la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02TD1756E:234b-5: dang po dka' thub la gnas pas /
T02TD1756E:234b-6: dur khrod la sogs pa'i gnas su /
T02TD1756E:234b-7: gcig tu dben par gnas pas /
T02TD1756E:234b-8: lus yongs su dag par byas la /
T02TD1756E:234b-10: aom ma h'a k'a la p'urba aindra bandha /
T02TD1756E:234b-12: pashci ma ba ru na bandha /
T02TD1756E:234b-13: be ra aa dhi pa ti bandha /
T02TD1756E:234b-14: a'i sha na bh'u ta aa dhi pa ti bandha /
T02TD1756E:234b-15: aa gni pee shva ra na /
T02TD1756E:234b-16: nee rri tye raksha sa bandha /
T02TD1756E:234b-17: b'a ya be b'a yu de ba ta /
T02TD1756E:234b-18: aurdhe si ta ma ho bandha /
T02TD1756E:234b-20: tsandra s'urya de ba gra ha /
T02TD1756E:234b-21: m'a tri dzra mi ka bh'u ta /
T02TD1756E:234b-22: ka ta p'u ta na shtsa dz'aksh'ashtar gha te /
T02TD1756E:234b-23: ye ka tsi ta dusht'a na /
T02TD1756E:234b-27: k'i la ya k'i la ya /
T02TD1756E:234b-28: badzra mung+ga re na ka ha ka ha shapta pa ta la /
T02TD1756E:234b-29: a'a ko ta ya a'a ko ta ya h'um phat phat sv'a h'a /
T02TD1756E:234b-31: de nas sngags bsgrub pa la sngags pas 'bad par bya ste /
T02TD1756E:234b-32: rang gi lus kyi snying gar yi ge ra yongs su gyur pa las /
T02TD1756E:234b-33: nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor gyi dbus su h'um sngon po las 'od zer 'phros pas /
T02TD1756E:234b-34: bla ma dang sangs rgyas byang chub sems dpa'i tshogs spyan drangs la /
T02TD1756E:234b-35: glang po che'i lta stangs tsam gyi nam mkha' la bzhugs su gsol te /
T02TD1756E:234b-37: me tog ma dang bdug spos ma sogs mchod pa'i lha mo rnams kyis mchod la /
T02TD1756E:234b-39: 'khor ba thog ma med pa nas //
T02TD1756E:234b-40: skye ba'i brgyud pa thams cad du //
T02TD1756E:234b-41: ji ltar byas pa'i sdig pa'i tshogs //
T02TD1756E:234b-42: byas dang rjes su yi rang ba //
T02TD1756E:234b-43: thams cad so sor bshags par bgyi //
T02TD1756E:234b-44: phyin chad bdag ni mi bgyid do //
T02TD1756E:234b-45: dkon mchog gsum la skyabs su mchi //
T02TD1756E:234b-46: mngon du thams cad so sor bshags //
T02TD1756E:234b-47: bsod nams kun la rjes yi rang //
T02TD1756E:234b-48: sangs rgyas byang chub yid kyis gzung //
T02TD1756E:235a-2: thog ma med pa'i 'khor ba nas //
T02TD1756E:235a-6: sring mo la sogs pas gtso byas pa'i sems can thams cad la ma bu gcig pa ltar byams pa'i sems ltar du gnas pas /
T02TD1756E:235a-7: 'khor ba'i pha rol tu bsgral bar bgyi'o //
T02TD1756E:235a-8: de ltar byams pa chen po'i sems dang ldan la /
T02TD1756E:235a-9: 'khor ba'i nags khrod nyam nga ba'am /
T02TD1756E:235a-10: sdug bsngal gyis gdungs pa'i sems can rnams yongs su bsgral ba'i blo bskyed la /
T02TD1756E:235a-11: sdug bsngal gyi rang bzhin la bsam ste /
T02TD1756E:235a-12: snying rje chen po bskyed la /
T02TD1756E:235a-13: dga' ba chen po'i sems kyis thams cad bde ba chen po'i sems dang ldan pas /
T02TD1756E:235a-14: kun la snyoms shing khyab par bya ste /
T02TD1756E:235a-15: de nas grub pa'i dpal nag po chen po'i gzugs rnyed pa dang ldan par bsams la /
T02TD1756E:235a-16: 'jig rten gyi chos brgyad rnam par spangs te /
T02TD1756E:235a-17: btang snyoms chen po'i sems su gnas par bya'o //
T02TD1756E:235a-18: de ltar tshangs pa'i gnas bzhi rab tu gnas par bya'o //
T02TD1756E:235a-19: de'i nang du rang gi lus kyi kun du spyod pa'i rang bzhin du blta bar bya ba dang /
T02TD1756E:235a-20: aom sv'a bh'a ba shuddha:sarba dharm'a:sv'a bh'a ba shuddhonyaham /
T02TD1756E:235a-21: aom sh'u n+ya t'a dzny'a na badzra sv'a bh'a ba a'atma konyaham /
T02TD1756E:235a-22: skad cig gis nam mkha'i dkyil du /
T02TD1756E:235a-23: sna tshogs padma'i lte ba la /
T02TD1756E:235a-24: yi ge ram las byung ba'i nyi ma dang h'um nag po yongs su rdzogs pa'i nag po chen po /
T02TD1756E:235a-25: bzang po'i dbang phyug phyag gnyis pa /
T02TD1756E:235a-29: mgo bo'i phreng bas brgyan pa /
T02TD1756E:235a-30: dbu skra dmar ser gyen du langs pa /
T02TD1756E:235a-32: mche ba rab tu gtsigs pa /
T02TD1756E:235a-33: 'jigs pa'i tshogs rnams kyang rab tu 'jigs par mdzad pa /
T02TD1756E:235a-34: klu brgyad kyis rnam par brgyan pa /
T02TD1756E:235a-37: mi bskyod bas rgyas btab pa /
T02TD1756E:235a-39: g-yon pa thod pa dang mchan khung na kha tv'am ga 'dzin pa /
T02TD1756E:235a-40: rab tu rngam pas khrag gsol zhing 'bo ba'i zhal can /
T02TD1756E:235a-41: ljags rnam par rol zhing bsgyur ba /
T02TD1756E:235a-42: mche ba rab tu gtsigs par rang nga nyid blta bar bya'o //
T02TD1756E:235b-0: ras ris la byas pa'i sku rnams kyi rang bzhin @235b yang de ltar yongs su rdzogs par bya'o //
T02TD1756E:235b-1: de dag mdun du 'dug pas kyang myur du 'grub pa yin te /
T02TD1756E:235b-4: yungs kar dkar po rnams gcig tu bsres te /
T02TD1756E:235b-5: btags pa'i sbos kyis bdug par bya ste /
T02TD1756E:235b-6: lugs ma dang thang sku la sogs pa yang bdug par bya'o //
T02TD1756E:235b-7: sran ma dang lhan cig btsos pa'i 'bras dang /
T02TD1756E:235b-13: de rnams kyis nag po chen po la gtor ma sbyin par bya'o //
T02TD1756E:235b-14: de rnams yongs su rdzogs nas /
T02TD1756E:235b-16: aom ma h'a k'a l'a ya h'um h'um phat phat sv'a h'a /
T02TD1756E:235b-17: 'di ni sngags kyi rgyal po dpag bsam gyi ljon shing ngam /
T02TD1756E:235b-18: yid bzhin gyi nor bu rin po che lta bu'o //
T02TD1756E:235b-19: snying ga dang kha nas mngon par 'thon te /
T02TD1756E:235b-20: lte ba'i padma la babs par bsam par bya'o //
T02TD1756E:235b-21: de yang myur ba ma yin cing bul ba yang ma yin la /
T02TD1756E:235b-22: yi ge 'bru yang ma lus par ma yengs par bzlas par bya'o //
T02TD1756E:235b-24: de ltar sngags kyi skyon thams cad spangs pa'o //
T02TD1756E:235b-25: mtshan mo'i thun gsum la gtor ma byin te /
T02TD1756E:235b-26: srod dang gung dang tho rangs kyi snang ba spangs pa'o //
T02TD1756E:235b-27: brtan pa'i sems kyis bzlas pas zla ba drug gis 'grub po //
T02TD1756E:235b-28: grub pa rnams kyang rab tu star zhing /
T02TD1756E:235b-29: grub pa rnams gang zhe na /
T02TD1756E:235b-30: dbang dang dgug pa dang por 'byung ngo //
T02TD1756E:235b-31: gnyis pa la rengs pa dang bskrad pa'o //
T02TD1756E:235b-32: gsum pa la dbye ba dang bsad pa /
T02TD1756E:235b-34: lnga pa la don thams cad 'grub po //
T02TD1756E:235b-35: de ltar grub pa brgyad grub nas /
T02TD1756E:235b-36: ji ltar chu klung gi rgyun 'gro zhing sgra sgrogs pa ltar /
T02TD1756E:235b-37: rtag tu nag po chen po sgrub pa'i rnal 'byor la brtson par bya'o //
T02TD1756E:235b-38: sems ma yangs par bsgrubs pas the tshom med par 'grub po //
T02TD1756E:235b-39: sems mi g-yo bas ni sangs rgyas kyi grub pa yang ster ro //
T02TD1756E:235b-40: de / nas gzhan brjod par bya ba /
T02TD1756E:235b-41: brtson 'grus kyis sngags pa'i 'bras bu brjod par bya ste /
T02TD1756E:235b-42: zla ba drug la rtsol ba byas te 'bum phrag gsum bzlas pas /
T02TD1756E:235b-43: blo gros rab tu rno bar 'gyur zhing /
T02TD1756E:236a-0: dri ma med cing kun du @236a * //
T02TD1756E:236a-1: rno ba'i shes rab dang ldan par 'gyur ro //
T02TD1756E:236a-3: lha rnams kyang dbang du 'gyur na /
T02TD1756E:236a-4: dman pa'i mi rnams smos ci dgos te /
T02TD1756E:236a-5: ji ltar byas pa bzhin du dbang du 'gyur ro //
T02TD1756E:236a-6: 'bum phrag dgu bzlas pas dug thams cad kyang dbang du 'gyur zhing /
T02TD1756E:236a-7: bsod nams dang grags pa chen po dang ldan par 'gyur ro //
T02TD1756E:236a-8: bye ba'i bar du bzlas na 'jig rten gsum dbang du 'gyur ro //
T02TD1756E:236a-9: bye ba gnyis bzlas na grub pa chen po dang ldan par 'gyur ro //
T02TD1756E:236a-10: ji ltar yid la bsams pa'i lha thams cad 'grub par 'gyur ro //
T02TD1756E:236a-11: sa brgyad kyi rnal 'byor kyang 'grub na /
T02TD1756E:236a-12: gzhan mang du brjod pas ci bya /
T02TD1756E:236a-15: rnam par grol ba'i sngags kyi rgyal bo 'di brjod pa'i mod la sdig pa thams cad kyang zad par byed la /
T02TD1756E:236a-16: rtag tu brgya phrag re bzlas pas kyang grub pa ster ro //
T02TD1756E:236a-17: khri phrag gcig gis bud med dbang du 'gyur zhing /
T02TD1756E:236a-18: 'bum phrag gcig gis rgyal po dbang du 'gyur la /
T02TD1756E:236a-19: 'bum phrag lngas lha dang gnod sbyin rnams nges par 'grub na /
T02TD1756E:236a-20: mi'i dpa' mo lta ci smos dbang gi sngags so //
T02TD1756E:236a-21: de nas las kyi rab tu dbye ba brjod par bya ste /
T02TD1756E:236a-22: las thams cad kyi 'bras bu ster ba ji ltar shes pa'i mod la myur du grub par 'gyur ro //
T02TD1756E:236a-23: aom kshi ha bu ha aa mu ka tsa ta ya h'um phat /
T02TD1756E:236a-24: khri phrag gcig bzlas pas dur khrod kyi rus pa la ling+ga byas nas dgra bo'i sgor sbas na zhag bdun gyis nges par skrod par 'gyur ro //
T02TD1756E:236a-25: aom mam dzham ksha aa mu kam stvam bha ya h'um phat /
T02TD1756E:236a-26: brgya phrag bzlas pas dgra bo rengs par 'gyur ro //
T02TD1756E:236a-27: aom dzra h'um ha stam stam bha ya h'um phat /
T02TD1756E:236a-28: byi ba'i rnga ma la lan bdun btab ste brgyab pas glang po che rengs par 'gyur ro //
T02TD1756E:236a-30: ba glang gi sha la btab ste brgyab na rta rengs par byed do //
T02TD1756E:236a-31: aom mu ham sarba shu na stvam bha ya mo ha ya h'um phat /
T02TD1756E:236a-32: stag gi pags pa la lan bdun bsngags te brgyab na /
T02TD1756E:236a-33: stag la sogs pa'i phyugs thams cad rengs par byed do //
T02TD1756E:236a-35: aom ma h'a nan ta h'um gtor ma la lan bdun bzlas te brgyab na sbrul rengs par byed do//
T02TD1756E:236b-0: @236b mi'i ngag bcing bar byed na /
T02TD1756E:236b-1: aom mu kha stvam bha ya aa mu ka sha bham phat /
T02TD1756E:236b-3: de nas gtor ma'i sngags ni /
T02TD1756E:236b-4: aom hra ka ha ka ha ma li ni mu khri pra sha tha ya pra sha tha ya /
T02TD1756E:236b-5: ma h'a k'a la bh'u ta aa dzra pra ho to shi m'a ra ya k'a ra ya k'a ra ya /
T02TD1756E:236b-6: sarba dushta pra dushta na grih na grihna /
T02TD1756E:236b-10: sh'i ghram da ha da ha /
T02TD1756E:236b-14: ai dam ba lim grihna grihna shi:sv'a h'a /
T02TD1756E:236b-15: sangs rgyas kyi bstan pa la gnod par byed pa dang /
T02TD1756E:236b-16: rtsod pa dang rab tu rtsod par byed pa rnams /
T02TD1756E:236b-17: mi'i thod pa'i nang du gtor ma khrag gis btab la sha'am sha chen pos brgyan pa nag po'i brgyad la sbyin par bya'o //
T02TD1756E:236b-18: de ma thag tu dgra bo 'khor dang bcas pa nyams par 'gyur ro //
T02TD1756E:236b-19: gzhan yang mig long ba dang /
T02TD1756E:236b-22: gnod pa chen po'i gtor ma'i cho ga'o //
T02TD1756E:236b-23: de nas sha za'i sgrub thabs brjod par bya ste /
T02TD1756E:236b-24: na mo ratna tra y'a ya /
T02TD1756E:236b-25: aom ma h'a k'a la pi sh'a ts'i ni s'a dha ya h'um h'um phat phat sv'a h'a /
T02TD1756E:236b-26: khri phrag gcig bzlas pas sngon du bsnyen par 'gyur ro //
T02TD1756E:236b-27: de nas sgrub thabs la 'jug par bya ste /
T02TD1756E:236b-28: aom kha ra mu khi ma h'a pi sh'a ts'i ni de hi da d'a bhya:sv'a h'a /
T02TD1756E:236b-29: sngags 'di nyi shu rtsa gcig gis lha la mngon par bsngags te /
T02TD1756E:236b-30: zla ba gcig gi bar du gtor ma'i snod du byin na /
T02TD1756E:236b-31: 'gron bu pa ni nyi shu rtsa gcig rtag tu ster bar 'gyur ro //
T02TD1756E:236b-32: nyin re bzhin du thos pa rtag tu spyad par bya ste /
T02TD1756E:236b-33: 'gron bu gcig lus na'ang phyis mi thob par 'gyur ro//
T02TD1756E:236b-35: aom aa na le kunda le grihna pinda pi sh'a ts'i ni sv'a h'a /
T02TD1756E:236b-36: lhag ma la lan bdun mngon par bsngags la /
T02TD1756E:236b-37: zhag bdun gyi bar du byin na /
T02TD1756E:236b-38: zla ba gsum gsum nas gos zung re ster bar 'gyur ro //
T02TD1756E:236b-40: aom aa la ghu sa ti grihnam pinda pi sh'a ts'i sv'a h'a /
T02TD1756E:236b-41: sngags 'di lan brgyad mngon par bsngags pas lhag ma zla ba gcig tu byin na /
T02TD1756E:236b-42: rtag tu gser ti na re ster bar 'gyur ro //
T02TD1756E:236b-43: rtag tu zad par spyad par bya'o //
T02TD1756E:236b-44: de nas dpa' mo la bya ba brjod par bya ste /
T02TD1756E:236b-45: aom ma h'a k'a la hrim hrim hrim ha sngags 'di brgya rtsa brgyad bzlas pas /
T02TD1756E:237a-1: aom tsa le tsa le tsi te tse do manytsa pa ya sv'a h'a /
T02TD1756E:237a-3: reg pa'i mod la bud med kyi khu ba 'pho zhing chags pa rab tu rgyas par 'gyur ro //
T02TD1756E:237a-6: shing thog bi dza p'u ra dang /
T02TD1756E:237a-8: de ltar rdzas bzhi mnyam par btags la /
T02TD1756E:237a-9: nag po chen po la spos kyis bdug par bya'o //
T02TD1756E:237a-10: aom ma h'a k'a la aa mu kam mun ma dam ku ru dza:dgra bo smyo zhing myos par 'gyur ro //
T02TD1756E:237a-11: skra bzhar na grol bar 'gyur ro //
T02TD1756E:237a-13: na ma:sarba bh'u te bhyo ga mi ni bha ma dzi l'a ya sv'a h'a /
T02TD1756E:237a-14: sngags 'di rgyab pa'i thal bas brgyab na dbang du 'gyur ro //
T02TD1756E:237a-15: thal ba bkrus pas ni grol bar 'gyur ro //
T02TD1756E:237a-16: de nas mi snang ba'i las la /
T02TD1756E:237a-17: na mo bo dhi sa tve bhya h'um shi gi ni sv'a h'a /
T02TD1756E:237a-18: de'i rjes la brgya phrag re bzlas pas /
T02TD1756E:237a-19: rgyal po thams cad kyi thig byas pas mgo rmongs par 'gyur ro //
T02TD1756E:237a-20: de'i tshe dbang gi rang bzhin du'ang 'gyur ro //
T02TD1756E:237a-22: yungs kar la mngon par bsngags te brgya rtsa brgyad kyi bzlas pa sgo la btab na sgo bye bar 'gyur ro //
T02TD1756E:237a-23: de nas rengs pa'i las la /
T02TD1756E:237a-24: na mo buddhe bhya:ta ta stvam bha ya dzam bha ya mo ha ya sv'a h'a /
T02TD1756E:237a-25: de'i rjes su khyo po dang bcas pa'i bram ze mo shi ba'i thal ba blangs te /
T02TD1756E:237a-26: brgya phrag gcig gis thal ba la bsngags te sangs rgyas gang la gtor ba de /
T02TD1756E:237a-27: sangs rgyas rengs par byed na bsod nams dman pa'i mi rnams la lta ci smos /
T02TD1756E:237a-28: sngags 'di brjod pa tsam gyis g-yul du zhugs pa'i mtshon cha thams cad kyang rengs par byed do //
T02TD1756E:237a-29: de nas me bsil bar bya ba'i las la /
T02TD1756E:237a-31: ru ha ya sa tsa ru ha dza mi dzva la ni /
T02TD1756E:237a-33: si ta lo mo bha ba tu sv'a h'a /
T02TD1756E:237a-34: de'i rjes su ma he'i mar blangs la /
T02TD1756E:237a-35: nags kyi spo ba rtsi sngo blangs la gcig tu btags te /
T02TD1756E:237a-36: rang gi lus po la byugs la sngags kyis mngon par btab ste /
T02TD1756E:237a-37: me'i nang du phyin yang lus po mi 'tshig par 'gyur ro //
T02TD1756E:237a-38: de nas rgyal po rengs pa'i las la /
T02TD1756E:237a-39: na mo ratna tra y'a ya /
T02TD1756E:237a-40: dza ya dza ya stam bha ni sv'a h'a /
T02TD1756E:237b-0: @237b sman tri sha ga ti'i rtsa ba blangs la brgya phrag gcig gis mngon par bsngags te /
T02TD1756E:237b-1: rgyal po rengs par byed do //
T02TD1756E:237b-2: de nas chu bcing bar byed pa'i cho ga la /
T02TD1756E:237b-3: na mo bha ga wa te /
T02TD1756E:237b-4: bighn'an dre dza lam pra bi sha me sv'a h'a /
T02TD1756E:237b-6: nya 'ud 'ud pa'i kha ru rin po che bcug la /
T02TD1756E:237b-7: rang gi lag par blangs te /
T02TD1756E:237b-8: chu'i steng du phyin pas chu bcing bar 'gyur ro //
T02TD1756E:237b-9: de nas bskrad par bya ba ni bya rog gi sgro blangs te /
T02TD1756E:237b-11: gang gi sgo ru sbas pas skrod par 'gyur ro //
T02TD1756E:237b-12: de bton na zhi bar 'gyur ro //
T02TD1756E:237b-14: na mo ratna tra y'a ya /
T02TD1756E:237b-15: tsa la pra tsa la sh'i ghram bha mi ni sv'a h'a /
T02TD1756E:237b-17: na mo ratna tra y'a ya /
T02TD1756E:237b-18: de ba ya ma h'a pre sha ka ma h'a bi lam su tu sv'a h'a /
T02TD1756E:237b-19: bram ze mo dang dge tshul dang /
T02TD1756E:237b-22: gang gi ming nas bzung te sa la sbas pa de thams cad dang 'khon par 'gyur ro //
T02TD1756E:237b-23: bton na ni grol bar 'gyur ro //
T02TD1756E:237b-24: de nas sbyin sreg gi las spyad par bya ste /
T02TD1756E:237b-25: ba glang gi sha chang gis bsres la thun gsum du bsregs pas /
T02TD1756E:237b-26: zla ba gcig gi nang du sangs rgyas kyang dbang du 'gyur na /
T02TD1756E:237b-27: mi'i dpa' mo lta ci smos /
T02TD1756E:237b-29: lan brgya'i bar du bsregs na ;
T02TD1756E:237b-30: / zla ba gsum gyis rags dang rgyud du bcas pa'i phongs pa spong bar 'gyur ro //
T02TD1756E:237b-31: bya rog gi sgro'i sbyin sreg la /
T02TD1756E:237b-32: mar khu chen po'i zhag la snag tsha byas la /
T02TD1756E:237b-33: aom ma h'a k'a la siddhi aanytsa dzny'a na s'a dh'a ya sv'a h'a /
T02TD1756E:237b-35: rtag tu mig la bskus nas mig sman du byas na /
T02TD1756E:237b-36: lkog tu gyur pa'i gter la sogs pa mthong bar 'gyur ro //
T02TD1756E:237b-37: de nas ral gri'i sgrub pa brjod de /
T02TD1756E:237b-38: 'od dang ldan pa'i lcags las gri brdungs la /
T02TD1756E:237b-39: lag pa g-yas pas bzung ste /
T02TD1756E:237b-40: nam mkha' la spyod pa'i mig gis dpral bar thig byas la /
T02TD1756E:237b-41: bram ze dkar po'i shing 'dab ma blangs la /
T02TD1756E:237b-42: sngon du mchod pa rgya chen po dbul bar bya'o //
T02TD1756E:237b-43: shing gi thig las lha ma byas la /
T02TD1756E:237b-44: ba glang gi ko bas sgregs te /
T02TD1756E:237b-46: de'i tshe thig grub par 'gyur ro //
T02TD1756E:237b-47: aom ma h'a k'a la siddha da da du ka s'a dha ya sv'a h'a /
T02TD1756E:238a-1: 'jig rten gsum gyi grub pa thams cad 'grub par 'gyur ro //
T02TD1756E:238a-2: nag po chen po'i rnal 'byor dang ldan pas so //
T02TD1756E:238a-3: 'bad pa dang rtsol ba chen pos mi sbyin cing sba bar bya'o //
T02TD1756E:238a-4: sbas shing mi sbyin par rtsol ba chen pos 'grub par 'gyur ro //
T02TD1756E:238a-5: smras shing byin na mi 'grub par 'gyur ro //
T02TD1756E:238a-6: dam tshig nyams pas mi 'grub par 'gyur ro //
T02TD1756E:238a-7: thams cad rab tu mi sbyin sba //
T02TD1756E:238a-8: sbyin bya rdo rje theg pa can //
T02TD1756E:238a-9: byed par ldan pa la sbyin zhing //
T02TD1756E:238a-10: de la sogs pa'i las rnams ni //
T02TD1756E:238a-11: rgyud kyi nang nas 'byung ba bzhin //
T02TD1756E:238a-12: de yi rang bzhin rnal 'byor pas //
T02TD1756E:238a-14: shes rab nag mo la ni 'khyud //
T02TD1756E:238a-15: legs pas mthun byed bdag la gus //
T02TD1756E:238a-16: rdo rje padma rab sbyor bas //
T02TD1756E:238a-17: 'jig rten gsum po stong par lta //
T02TD1756E:238a-18: stong nyid ngo bo nyid stong pas //
T02TD1756E:238a-19: stong pa chen po thams cad stong //
T02TD1756E:238a-20: 'jig rten gsum po bdag med pas //
T02TD1756E:238a-21: bde ba chen po bya ba yin //
T02TD1756E:238a-22: rtsol bas sangs rgyas thob par 'gyur //
T02TD1756E:238a-23: rang bzhin med pas sgrib kun spangs //
T02TD1756E:238a-24: ye shes sku ste spro bsdu ba //
T02TD1756E:238a-25: 'gro ba pha rol yid dang sbyor //
T02TD1756E:238a-26: de nas las thams cad 'grub pa'i gtor ma sbyin te /
T02TD1756E:238a-33: aashta n'a ga de ba dza ksha r'a ksha sa /
T02TD1756E:238a-40: phum phem ma h'atta h'a sa /
T02TD1756E:238a-41: gha dza gha dzha krishna bha sna ya phrem phrem sv'a h'a /
T02TD1756E:238a-43: sran ma bsres pa'i thug pa dang /
T02TD1756E:238a-46: zan gyis snod rab tu gang bar byas te /
T02TD1756E:238a-47: de ltar gtor ma byin pas zhag nyi shu rtsa gcig na legs pa dang nyes pa ston par 'gyur ro //
T02TD1756E:238a-48: zla ba gcig tu byin na don thams cad 'grub par 'gyur ro //
T02TD1756E:238a-49: lo gcig gi bar du byin pas /
T02TD1756E:238a-50: ji ltar yid la bsams pa 'grub par 'gyur ro //
T02TD1756E:238a-51: aom ka r'a la bi ka r'a la /
T02TD1756E:238a-56: kshim shrim tsanda tsanda mam ham h'um /
T02TD1756E:238a-57: ma h'a nandve shva r'a ya sv'a h'a /
T02TD1756E:238a-58: sngags 'di lan bdun gyi bar du chu la btab ste gdong bkru bar bya'o //
T02TD1756E:238a-59: mi thams cad mthun par 'gyur ro //
T02TD1756E:238a-60: dgra bo thams cad rmongs par 'gyur ro //
T02TD1756E:238b-0: aom ma h'a @238b k'a la hrim hrim hrim phat sv'a h'a /
T02TD1756E:238b-1: thams cad 'grub par byed pa'i sngags so //
T02TD1756E:238b-3: de nas rang ris bri ba'i cho ga brjod par bya'o //
T02TD1756E:238b-4: rigs lnga'i bud med kyi zla mtshan blang la mar khu chen po dang bsres te /
T02TD1756E:238b-5: ro bsregs pa'i shul du bzhag la /
T02TD1756E:238b-6: nag po'i brgyad kyi nang du thun gnyis pa'i gung la ri mo byed pa dbang bskur dang ldan pas /
T02TD1756E:238b-7: chang 'thungs na mig dmar por gyur pas /
T02TD1756E:238b-8: dam tshig gi rdzas ci 'byor pa'i mchod pa bshams te /
T02TD1756E:238b-10: sngon du brjod pa ltar nag po chen po bri bar bya'o //
T02TD1756E:238b-11: nag po'i phyogs kyi mtshams bcu bzhi la bri bar bya'o //
T02TD1756E:238b-12: rtsi la dngul gyis kyang bsres te /
T02TD1756E:238b-13: thun gnyis pa la mig la bskus la /
T02TD1756E:238b-14: rab tu gnas pa yang de nyid la'o //
T02TD1756E:238b-15: ji ltar 'byor pa'i stobs kyis bla ma mchod la /
T02TD1756E:238b-16: gus pas sgrub thabs bstan par bya'o //
T02TD1756E:238b-18: gtor ma la sogs pa'i yo byad dang ldan pas /
T02TD1756E:238b-19: sngon du bsnyen pa 'bum phrag gsum bya'o //
T02TD1756E:238b-20: de nas 'bum phrag gcig bzlas pas 'grub par 'gyur ro //
T02TD1756E:238b-21: thams cad kyi bya ba byed par 'gyur ro //
T02TD1756E:238b-22: sems can thams cad kyi don byed pa'i sangs rgyas su 'gyur ro //
T02TD1756E:238b-23: nag po chen po'i sgrub thabs rdzogs so /
T02TD1756E:238b-25: // / phyag rgya chen po mchog gi dngos grub thob pa'i dpal lhan cig skyes pa'i zhabs kyis mdzad pa'o //
T02TD1756E:238b-26: rgya gar gyi mkhan po shr'i na rendra bha dra dang /
T02TD1756E:238b-27: bod kyi lo ts'a ba au rgyan pa rin chen dpal gyis /
T02TD1756E:238b-28: ri bo chen po spu tra'i mgul du bsgyur ba'o//
